7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Hypotenuse AI and Simplified share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form, Templates, Tone Control. Where Hypotenuse AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Seo Tools and Plagiarism Check and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Hypotenuse AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Simplified scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Simplified comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Hypotenuse AI begins at $29/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Hypotenuse AI's free tier and Simplified's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
